 Twitch 因人工智能问题取消裸体艺术新规定https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=twitch-rolls-back-新裸体艺术规则对人工智能的关注Ali ShutlerMon, 18 Dec 2023 12:04:52 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsAIVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3560354 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="抽搐" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们走得太远了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354">Twitch 因人工智能担忧而取消裸体艺术新规定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="抽搐" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Twitch-Credit-Ink-Drop-Alamy-Stock-Photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于对<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ai">人工智能</a>的担忧， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/twitch">Twitch</a>被迫改变流媒体平台上裸体艺术的新的、宽松的指导方针。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/how-ai-is-pushing-the-boundaries-of-entertainment-3409263">超越人类想象：人工智能如何突破娱乐界限</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周，Twitch 对性内容和裸露的指导方针进行了几处修改，禁止了一些使用摄像机角度使其看起来像是赤裸上身的主播 [来自<a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/twitch-relaxes-about-nudity-after-viral-topless-streams-says-you-can-be-sexy-on-stream-so-long-as-its-artistic-or-fictionalized/">PC Gamer</a> ]。</p><p>新规则包括对乳房和生殖器的“绘画、动画或雕刻”描绘采取更宽松的立场，并允许“对裸体的艺术描绘”。</p><p> “这次更新的一部分包括改变我们对待虚构裸体的方式，”Twitch 在<a href="https://safety.twitch.tv/s/article/Sexual-Content-Policy-Update?language=en_US">博客</a>中写道。 “多年来，我们从艺术家那里听到我们的内容政策受到限制。在进行此更新时，我们试图响应这些请求，并允许 Twitch 上蓬勃发展的艺术家社区在他们的艺术中利用人类形态。”</p><p>然而，就在新规则生效两天后，Twitch<a href="https://x.com/Twitch/status/1735677597831356789" target="_blank" rel="noopener">确认</a>将取消部分更改。 </p><figure id="attachment_3453188" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3453188" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3453188" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy.jpg" alt="Twitch 主播反对该公司新的品牌内容政策，现在该政策已被撤回。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/twitch-streamers-protest-branded-content-policy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3453188" class="wp-caption-text">人们玩电子游戏。图片来源：Ron Lach，来自 Pexels</figcaption></figure><p> Twitch 表示：“经过反思，我们认为这一改变太过分了。” “裸体的数字描绘提出了一个独特的挑战——人工智能可以用来创建逼真的图像，而且很难区分数字艺术和摄影。”</p><p> “因此，从今天起，我们将取消艺术裸体的变化。展望未来，无论采用何种媒体，Twitch 上都将不允许出现真实或虚构的裸体描述。”该平台在为更新造成的混乱致歉之前确认道。</p><p>去年 12 月，数百名艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/artists-protest-use-of-ai-generated-artwork-on-portfolio-site-artstation-3366778">在专业作品集网站 Artstation 上抗议使用人工智能创作的艺术作品</a>。</p><p>在其他消息中，Larian 首席执行官 Swen Vincke 表示， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/baldurs-gate-iii">《博德之门 3》</a></em>永远不会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-will-never-come-to-xbox-game-pass-3560347">发布</a>。 “我们制作了一款大型游戏，所以我认为为此付出的代价是合理的。这让我们能够继续制作其他游戏。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/twitch-rolls-back-new-nude-art-rules-over-ai-concerns-3560354">Twitch 因人工智能担忧而取消裸体艺术新规定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《小丑》将于 2024 年在皇家节日音乐厅放映，现场管弦乐队演奏电影配乐https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-to-be-screened-at-royal-festival-hall-with-live-orchestra-3560339?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=joker-to-be-在皇家节日大厅与现场管弦乐团放映Damian JonesMon, 18 Dec 2023 11:57:40 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsDC Extended Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3560339 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小丑播放列表" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>门票将于本周晚些时候发售</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-to-be-screened-at-royal-festival-hall-with-live-orchestra-3560339">《小丑》将于 2024 年在皇家节日音乐厅放映，并由现场管弦乐队演奏电影配乐，该影片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="小丑播放列表" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/joker_03-920x460-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/dc-extended-universe">DC</a> 2019 年电影<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/joker-folie-a-deux">《小丑》</a></em>将在伦敦皇家节日音乐厅放映，现场管弦乐队将演奏作曲家 Hildur Guðnadóttir 的获奖配乐。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/joker-2-folie-a-deux-title-release-date-cast-plot-3249040">这是我们对《小丑》续集的了解</a></strong></li></ul><p>该节目名为“<em>小丑</em><i>–</i>现场”<i> </i>In Concert&#39;将于2024年2月7日星期三在该场地上演。</p><p>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-to-be-screened-in-concert-venues-with-a-live-orchestra-composing-hildur-gudnadottirs-score-2925240">2021 年在英国举办的上一个音乐会系列的</a>延续。</p><p>预售门票于本周三（12 月 20 日）上午 10 点（格林威治标准时间）开始发售，然后在第二天（12 月 21 日）开始全面发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2F" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。 </p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://ecp.yusercontent.com/mail?url=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fcision-attachments-uk%2Fem5rp6jio441nxkxr41brtyk6f0v&amp;t=1702894408&amp;ymreqid=7d300e6f-2dd5-6f8f-1cda-87004601c800&amp;sig=wb3T8xUc2qV7krRGjAhL8Q--~D" /></p><p> <em>《NME》</em>此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joaquin-phoenix">对华金·菲尼克斯</a>主演的这部电影进行了评价，给予<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/joker-review-a-melancholic-psychodrama-punctuated-by-splashes-of-shocking-violence-2543865">其四星评价</a>，并称这是一部“忧郁的心理剧，不时夹杂着令人震惊的暴力事件”。</p><p>它补充道：“托德·菲利普斯并不是在开玩笑。这是令人兴奋的事情。这非常出色。”</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">雷德利·斯科特</a>最近批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ridley-scott-criticises-joker-for-celebrating-violence-3511788">这部电影“庆祝暴力的方式”</a> 。他在一次新的采访中解释说，虽然他的表演给他留下了深刻的印象，但他并不是整部电影的最大粉丝。</p><p> “我被他令人震惊的电影<em>《小丑》</em>震惊了，”这位电影制片人告诉<a href="https://deadline.com/2023/10/ridley-scott-napoleon-joaquin-phoenix-casting-joker-gladiator-1235566587/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a> 。 “我不喜欢它庆祝暴力的方式，但华金很了不起。”</p><p>尽管如此，斯科特此前曾谈到，他在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/napoleon">拿破仑</a></em>的<em>小丑</em>表演中受到了启发，决定聘请菲尼克斯，他告诉<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/ridley-scott-napoleon-psyche-emperor-exclusive-image/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《帝国》</em></a> ：“我盯着华金说，‘这个小恶魔就是拿破仑·波拿巴。’”他长得很像他。”</p><p>在其他地方，正在创作续集<em>《小丑：双人舞曲》</em>的古兹纳多蒂尔也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-2-composer-teases-a-lot-of-music-in-sequel-3494207">开玩笑说，这可能比预期更像一部音乐剧</a>。</p><p> “我只能说将会有很多音乐，”古兹纳多蒂尔说。 “这就是我所能给予的一切。”</p><p>菲尼克斯回归饰演亚瑟·弗莱克， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>饰演哈莉·奎茵。续集的拍摄<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lady-gaga-wraps-filming-on-joker-2-with-new-look-harley-quinn-3427441">已于今年四月正式杀青</a>。续集的新演员阵容包括布莱丹·格里森、凯瑟琳·基纳、雅各布·洛夫兰和哈里·劳蒂。</p><p> <em>《小丑：双人舞》</em>计划于 2024 年 10 月 4 日在电影院上映。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/joker-to-be-screened-at-royal-festival-hall-with-live-orchestra-3560339">《小丑》将于 2024 年在皇家节日音乐厅放映，并由现场管弦乐队演奏电影配乐，该影片</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
